# Local PNG sprite art for the image protocols (kitty / iTerm2). This is
# scratch art for testing only and is replaced in a follow-up change, so it is
# never committed. The committed default avatar is the kaomoji set in
# emotes/ascii/ascii.yaml, which the renderer falls back to whenever a set has
# no PNG frames.
emotes/default/
emotes/**/*.png
emotes/**/emotes.json
